<reference id="strow" xml:lang="en-us">
   <title>
      <keyword>strow</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>simpletable</keyword>&gt; row (&lt;<keyword>strow</keyword>&gt;) element specifies
a row in a simple table, like row in a conventional <ph>
         <xref href="table.xml">table</xref>
      </ph>.</shortdesc>
